                            ],
                            "value": "increment 300 feet"
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "If you loaded at least 70 hwacha arrows, the area increases to a 25-foot burst. If you loaded 100 hwacha arrows, the area increases to a 30-foot burst and the damage to 5d8 piercing.",
